#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please note that there is no session or conversation context available when "
"a message is delivered to a message-driven bean. Only "
"<literal>@RequestScoped</literal> and <literal>@ApplicationScoped</literal> "
"beans are available."
